Get current time and set those values to your selected date

```
&lt;Flatpickr
          placeholder=&quot;Select date&quot;
          ref={datepickerRef}
          options={options}
          value={props.field.value ? props.field.value : &#39;&#39;}
          onChange={(date) =&gt; {
            let selectedDate = date[0];
            let currentDate = new Date();
